Skills/Experience Requirements:
Expertise in digital marketing analytics, including website, mobile, social media, search and display;
Experience with digital analytics tools, platforms, and infrastructure;
Experience in developing strategic analytical roadmaps and managing teams to effectively deliver the roadmap;
Advanced understanding of marketing principles, analytic strategies and cross-channel marketing measurement;
Strong analytical skills i.e. able to analyze raw data, draw conclusions, and develop actionable recommendations experience in the analysis of large data sets to find useful relationships.
