COMPETENCIES (SKILLS) REQUIRED: * Ability to influence change within a broad management group. * Project management skills. * The ability to perform within a demanding environment in which creativity, motivation, intelligence and an optimistic sense of purpose are extremely important. * Excellent analytical and planning ability. * Possess superior verbal and written communication skills, along with the ability to listen. * Outstanding organization skills and the ability to function effectively without a large support structure. * High level of maturity, tact, sensitivity and diplomacy and the ability to work within a diverse setting. DESIRED EDUCATION/CERTIFICATION/USEFUL PRIOR JOB EXPERIENCE: * College degree preferably in business management. * 5-10 years of management experience.
